Now lay this fact to heartï¼š the ever virgin is never fruitful. To be fruitful
the soul must be wife. Spouse is the noblest title of the soul, nobler than
virgin. For a man to receive God within him is good and in receiving he is
virgin. But for God to be fruitful in him is still better.
